participant_id.Description: Unique BIDS identifier for the participant in this study.

subjectkey.Description: The NDAR Global Unique Identifier (GUID) for research subject

src_subject_id.Description: Subject ID how it's defined in lab/project

interview_date.Description: Date on which the interview/genetic test/sampling/imaging/biospecimen was completed. MM/DD/YYYY

interview_age.Description: Age in months at the time of the interview/test/sampling/imaging. | Age is rounded to chronological month. If the research participant is 15-days-old at time of interview, the appropriate value would be 0 months. If the participant is 16-days-old, the value would be 1 month.

sex.Description: Sex of subject at birth | M = Male; F = Female; O=Other; NR = Not reported

eventname.Description: The event name for which the data was collected

gish2_had_bf_gf.Description: Have you ever had a boyfriend or girlfriend? | 1=Yes; 0=No; 777=Refuse to Answer

gish2_want_bf_gf.Description: Have you ever wanted to have a boyfriend or girlfriend? | 1=Yes; 0=No; 777=Refuse to Answer

gish2_nr_kiss.Description: Have you ever kissed a boy or girl on the mouth? | 1=Yes; 0=No; 777=Refuse to answer

gish2_nr_hands.Description: Has a boy or girl ever put their hands under your clothes? | 1=Yes; 0=No; 777=Refuse to answer

gish2_nr_self_hands.Description: Have you ever put your hands under a boy's or girl's clothes? | 1=Yes; 0=No; 777=Refuse to answer

gish2_cf_have_bf_gf.Description: Having a boyfriend or girlfriend | 1=Approve; 2=Neither Approve / Disapprove; 3=Disapprove; 999=Don't Know; 777=Refuse to Answer

gish2_cf_kiss.Description: Kissing a boy or girl on the mouth | 1=Approve; 2=Neither Approve / Disapprove; 3=Disapprove; 999=Don't Know; 777=Refuse to Answer

gish2_cf_hands.Description: A boy or girl putting their hands under your clothes | 1=Approve; 2=Neither Approve / Disapprove; 3=Disapprove; 999=Don't Know; 777=Refuse to Answer

gish2_cf_self_hands.Description: Putting your hands under a boy's or girl's clothes? | 1=Approve; 2=Neither Approve / Disapprove; 3=Disapprove; 999=Don't Know; 777=Refuse to Answer

gish2_f_had_bf_gf.Description: Had a boyfriend/girlfriend | 1=None; 2=A Few; 3=Most; 4=All; 999=Don't Know; 777=Refuse to Answer

gish2_f_kiss.Description: Kissed a boy or a girl on the mouth | 1=None; 2=A Few; 3=Most; 4=All; 999=Don't Know; 777=Refuse to Answer

gish2_f_hands.Description: Had a boy or girl put their hands under your friend's clothes. | 1=None; 2=A Few; 3=Most; 4=All; 999=Don't Know; 777=Refuse to Answer

gish2_f_self_hands.Description: Put their hands under a boy's or girl's clothes | 1=None; 2=A Few; 3=Most; 4=All; 999=Don't Know; 777=Refuse to Answer
